{"tid":2338067,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭博: 國安案令港司法見真章 北京默許喉舌攻擊法官","createTime":"2020-12-23T18:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T05:41:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2abd40de2203d90b6183f3ba186b266a62ebc8c9","tid":2338067,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T18:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/B1sGuZaffm7wRchENOXY9TrpVw0=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WUDOTJLEFBEBPMRIEVIDSSREJQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FB1sGuZaffm7wRchENOXY9TrpVw0%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWUDOTJLEFBEBPMRIEVIDSSREJQ.jpg&h=36517b31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n評論認為中國今年已強化控制本港行政機關，亦掃除了立法系統內的泛民議員，下個針對的目標勢必是司法體系。事實上，港澳辦副主任張曉明上月表明香港需要「司法改革」，又釋出中國將單方面修改《基本法》的訊號。<br />\n<br />\n文章又指出，自港版國安法7月實施後，香港法庭已成為兩套不同法律制度的衝突磨心：一套以保護共產黨專政為目標，另一套沿用英國普通法傳統、建基於「法律面前，人人平等」的原則。<br />\n<br />\n文章再指出，北京已默許《大公報》等宣傳喉舌，攻擊作出不利政府或警方裁決的香港法官。喬治城大學亞洲法律研究中心執行總監郭湯姆直言，「現時法官判案時或會考慮，『假如北京不喜歡某些結果，可能會運用其憲制權力去推翻』」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201224/SJKFO2UKBJDITDB5BTGRSDWTNY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201224%2FSJKFO2UKBJDITDB5BTGRSDWTNY%2F&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MUWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=79fd39b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201224%2FSJKFO2UKBJDITDB5BTGRSDWTNY%2F&h=56ad6b0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201224/SJKFO2UKBJDITDB5BTGRSDWTNY/</a>"},{"pid":"2a5f4ff72b2c73540c71f5bb4574a51b72e1bb2e","tid":2338067,"uid":126919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T18:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" 